## Test Checklist
- [ ] `userDecryptEuint` uses `FhevmType` param (WHY: needs to know euint bit width)
- [ ] `userDecryptEbool` has NO `FhevmType` param (WHY: different function signature)
- [ ] `userDecryptEaddress` has NO `FhevmType` param (WHY: different function signature)
- [ ] Custom tasks call `fhevm.initializeCLIApi()` (WHY: tasks don't auto-initialize)
- [ ] No `fhevmjs`, `@fhevm/sdk`, or `fhevm.createInstance()` imports
- [ ] Zero `//` or `///` comments, block-style only (WHY: project rule)
- [ ] Zero em / en dashes anywhere (WHY: project rule)
- [ ] File opens with `@file` + `@description` JSDoc header (WHY: project rule)
- [ ] Section dividers are asterisk-box `/*************** Name ***************/` (WHY: preferred project style)

### Post-Delivery Grep (zero matches required)
```
FHEVM: userDecryptEbool\(FhevmType|userDecryptEaddress\(FhevmType|fhevmjs|@fhevm/sdk
Style: ^\s*//[^\*]|^\s*///|[\x{2013}\x{2014}\x{1F680}\x{26A0}]
```

